snippet.title: Tavernacle - Official Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Here's your look at Tavernacle!, an upcoming multiplayer game where you play as dwarves, gather supplies, and craft towers to protect your brewery. 

Explore the world and learn to cooperate to achieve victory in this chaotic multiplayer game. Tavernacle! launches on Steam in early 2023. A Steam Next Fest demo is available now.
